sourcesContent: function t(t){let n={name:"string",version:"string",chainId:"uint256",verifyingContract:"address",salt:"bytes32"},e=t.types.EIP712Domain??Object.entries(t.domain??{}).map((([t,e])=>{if(null!=e&&"string"==typeof t&&t in n)return{name:t,type:n[t]}})).filter((t=>!!t)),i={...t.types};return i.EIP712Domain=e,{...t,types:i}}export{t as generateDomainType};
